text: Steven Caldwell (born 1980) is a Scottish football defender. Steven or Stephen Caldwell may also refer to: *Stephen A. Caldwell (1889–1956), American educator *Steven Caldwell (Stargate), a fictional character from the American television show Stargate ==See also== *Steve Cardwell (born 1950), Canadian ice hockey player *Terran Trade Authority, a science-fiction setting written by Stewart Cowley, who also wrote under the pseudonym "Steven Caldwell"
title: Steven Caldwell (disambiguation)
